title: Stink Monster
description: Thomas and the other young engines encounter a stink monster that threatens to spread a stench all over Knapford! When Percy is kidnapped by the stink monster, the rest of the Biggest Adventure Club band together to create a plan to save their friend and stop the stink monster in its tracks! Looking closer, they realize it's their good friend Whiff's new invention causing a stink!
seriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Brand New Track

Everything seems new and exciting, and even a night spent stuck in the mud turns into a wonderful experience. Only in the light of day do they realize that nothing they saw was really "new" at all - it just seemed so because they brought to it a sense of delight and discovery.

title: Christmas Mountain

They get creative to keep a disappointed Bruno's holiday spirit bright, ultimately transforming Lookout Mountain into the best -- and biggest -- replacement "tree!" Thomas, Percy, and Bruno are joined by their friends to decorate, sing, and celebrate the tradition together!

Sandy and Carly show up to teach Thomas that everyone needs a little help sometimes, and the three watch as all the engines on Sodor team up to complete the delivery.
